Comment: 1,0:01:57.74,0:02:01.89,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,TẬP 11\NPHI HÀNH ĐOÀN GÀN DỞ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.59,0:02:05.83,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Space travel log 0968.}{\i0}{\i1}Nhật ký du hành vũ trụ 0968.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:12.29,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We were wasting our free time.}{\i0}Gọi săn tiền thưởng\N {\i1}{bounty-hunting job a "freelance" job,}{\i0}là làm nghề tự do thì nghe có vẻ hay ho,
Comment: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:09.59,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{We were wasting our free time.}{\i0}Gọi săn tiền thưởng
Comment: 0,0:02:09.59,0:02:12.29,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{bounty-hunting job a "freelance" job,}{\i0}là làm nghề tự do thì nghe có vẻ hay ho,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:17.03,Main,combine,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but all that means is that we're self-employed.}{\i0}nhưng thật ra nó có nghĩa là tự mình làm chủ.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When we have no jobs, we have none at all.}{\i0}{\i1}Và khi không có việc{\i0}\N{\i1}thì không có gì để làm cả.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.09,0:02:22.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Well, that's all a part of our destiny,}{\i0}{\i1}Đó là số phận của chúng tôi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{but it's troublesome that we're out of money.}{\i0}{\i1}Nhưng thật khó khăn khi không tiền.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{And so, we get urges to make quick cash...}{\i0}Nên cuối cùng chúng tôi cũng cố\Nlàm việc vặt kiếm vài đồng lẻ, nhưng...
Comment: 0,0:02:25.89,0:02:31.08,Main,,0,0,0,,BÀI HỌC 1
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.92,0:02:37.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Any problem with using these?}Sẵn sàng chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.72,0:02:44.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{Evens!}Chẵn!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.23,Main,,0,0,0,,{Evens, is it?}Chẵn ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:51.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{No, odds after all!}Không, là lẻ!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.69,0:02:56.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{Odds, is it?}Lẻ ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.15,0:02:59.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah... odds.}Ừ, lẻ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:04.08,Main,,0,0,0,,{Double ace, even.}Mắt rắn, chẵn!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:23.77,Main,,0,0,0,,{I can't eat any more...}Mình không ăn nổi nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:28.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{Well, it would be easiest for me\Nif you paid up in cash.}Anh trả bằng tiền mặt thì dễ cho tôi hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.73,0:03:30.91,Main,,0,0,0,,{So, what'll it be?}Vậy sao đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:35.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{A man does not take back his word!}Nam nhi đại trượng phu phải giữ lời.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.13,0:03:45.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's why I told you not to do it.}Đó là lý do tôi bảo anh đừng chơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.32,0:04:19.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{sweat for their money after all.}{\i0}{\i1}Cái câu làm đổ mồ hôi{\i0}\N{\i1}sôi nước mắt đúng là thật mà.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.85,0:04:21.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{Those that try to get rich quick}{\i0}{\i1}Những người cố làm giàu không chính đáng{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.94,0:04:25.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{or live at the expense of others}{\i0}{\i1}hoặc sống dựa dẫm người khác{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.85,0:04:28.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{somewhere along the way.}{\i0}{\i1}đều sẽ sớm bị quả báo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.38,0:04:31.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That is the lesson...}{\i0}{\i1}Bài học là thế.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:36.42,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But one thing about humans is that they}{\i0}Nhưng phàm ở đời,\N {\i1}{lessons they just learned.}{\i0}học rồi lại quên là chuyện thường tình.
Comment: 0,0:04:32.07,0:04:34.33,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But one thing about humans is that they}{\i0}Nhưng phàm ở đời,
Comment: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:36.42,Main,split,0,0,0,,{\i1}{lessons they just learned.}{\i0}học rồi lại quên là chuyện thường tình.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.12,0:04:40.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{Dammit.}Chết tiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:47.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{There was a fridge way back here?}Có cái tủ lạnh ở đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:05:01.28,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{"Survival of the fittest" is the law of the land.}{\i0}{\i1}Mạnh được yếu thua{\i0}\N{\i1}là chuyện hiển nhiên ở đời.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.68,0:05:04.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{To fool and to be fooled is the reason we live.}{\i0}{\i1}Ta sống để lừa và bị lừa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.71,0:05:08.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{happen to me when I trust others.}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi chưa bao giờ gặp cái kết có hậu{\i0}\N{\i1}khi tin người.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:10.70,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That's the lesson.}{\i0}{\i1}Bài học là thế.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:19.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{How much did you swindle?}Lừa được bao nhiêu tiền rồi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.22,0:05:21.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Would you stop saying things\Nthat would hurt my reputation?}Thôi nói những điều\Ngây tổn hại danh tiếng của tôi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.73,0:05:23.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{He lost on his own!}Tự anh ấy thua mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{Because he couldn't\Nsee through this cheat?}Anh ấy không thấy mánh lới của cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.60,0:05:30.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's part of one's skill to see through it.}Nhận ra mánh lới là một phần của trò chơi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.71,0:05:32.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{At least give his clothes back to him.}Ít nhất thì trả lại quần áo cho anh ấy đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'll lend them to him.}Tôi sẽ cho anh ấy thuê lại.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.25,0:05:35.94,Main,,0,0,0,,{Greedy, aren't we?}Tham lam quá nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.94,0:05:38.48,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's rough out there in the real world.}Thế giới ngoài kia tàn bạo lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, what's up?}Này, sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:52.62,Main,,0,0,0,,{Something bit me.}Có thứ gì cắn tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.62,0:05:54.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{What do you mean, "something"?}Thứ gì là sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{It wasn't a rat!}Không phải chuột!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.39,Main,,0,0,0,,{Look at this! This wound on my neck!}Nhìn vết cắn trên cổ tôi nè!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.27,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is silly. It was a waste\Nof time running over here.}Ngớ ngẩn. Thật phí thời gian chạy qua đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.85,0:06:18.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{Spike! I was bitten around that fridge!}Spike! Tôi bị cắn gần cái tủ lạnh đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:20.09,Main,,0,0,0,,{Fridge?}Tủ lạnh ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.09,0:06:23.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hmm? You have a clue?}Cậu biết gì về nó không?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.13,0:06:26.61,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm sure... there was something...}Giờ anh nhắc...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.57,0:06:29.07,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nope, can't remember.}Không. Không nhớ nổi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:56.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{You sure this is gonna work?}Cậu chắc có tác dụng chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{It works on everything but\Nmyopia and cavities. [original: "The only things it doesn't work on are nearsightedness and cavities."]}Chỉ cận thị và sâu răng\Nlà không chữa được thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.19,0:07:01.18,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Then it works on athlete's foot?}Nấm ở chân cũng chữa được à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.18,0:07:02.00,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Of course.}Tất nhiên.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.95,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't you have something more\Nlegit that would get rid of sores?}Không có thứ gì hợp pháp hơn\Nví dụ như thuốc mỡ kháng sinh à?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.95,0:07:06.90,Main,,0,0,0,,{That would be this.}Ừ, cái này.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.85,0:07:09.98,Main,split,0,0,0,,{That gets rid of sores?}Đó là thuốc mỡ kháng sinh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:10.61,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{Crush this, and you boil it\Nin 3 cups of water until}Nghiền nó, {the liquid simmers down\Nto 1 cup, and you drink it.}đun với ba chén nước\N cho đến khi sắc lại còn một chén, rồi uống.
Comment: 0,0:07:11.02,0:07:13.86,Main,,0,0,0,,{Crush this, and you boil it\Nin 3 cups of water until}Nghiền nó, đun với ba chén nước cho đến khi
Comment: 0,0:07:13.86,0:07:16.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{the liquid simmers down\Nto 1 cup, and you drink it.}sắc lại còn một chén, rồi uống.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.80,0:07:19.37,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Spike, isn't there something more...}Spike, không còn thứ gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.12,Main,split,0,0,0,,{different?}khác sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, I got just the thing.}Đây chính là thứ anh cần.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:23.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{Yeah, gimme that.}Tôi sẽ dùng nó!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.65,0:07:27.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Gimme what you had before.}Đưa tôi thứ trước đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.37,0:07:39.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey... I'm feeling a lot sicker now...}Này, tôi bắt đầu thấy tệ hơn rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.10,0:07:41.35,Main,,0,0,0,,{Do I look pale?}Trông mặt tôi xanh xao không?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{You're pretty pale to begin with.}Anh xanh xao từ đầu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.36,0:07:46.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{What is this awful smell?}Mùi gì kinh thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.73,0:07:47.79,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Herbal medicine.}Thảo dược.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:49.69,Main,split,0,0,0,,{This?}{\i0}Thảo dược? Cái này ư?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:54.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{It smells like you just left a rag\Nthat cleaned up spilt milk out to dry!}Mùi như phơi cái nùi giẻ đầy sữa vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.11,0:07:57.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{I think it's more like rotten soybeans.}Không, tôi nghĩ mùi nó\Ngiống đậu nành lên men hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.16,Main,,0,0,0,,{Knock it off! I have to drink this ya know!}Thôi ngay đi!\NMấy người biết tôi phải uống nó mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh brother.}Trời ơi.\NNày.
