Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.24,Main,split,0,0,0,,{There's nothing to make a fuss about.}Không cần làm quá như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.50,0:08:41.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Am I wrong?}Tôi nói sai à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.00,0:08:42.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{I have no clue.}Tôi không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.63,0:08:45.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{He seems to have gotten some poison\Nthat's not in this database.}Có vẻ là một chất độc\Nkhông có trong hệ thống dữ liệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.91,0:08:48.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Looking at similar poisons...}Thứ gần giống nhất có vẻ là...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.46,0:08:50.46,Main,,0,0,0,,{Cryptosporidium...}Cryptosporidium.
Comment: 1,0:08:50.49,0:08:51.41,Main,from_ocr,0,0,0,,KHÔNG KHỚP
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.50,0:08:52.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's not it.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.55,0:08:54.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{Cholera?}Bệnh tả à?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.83,0:08:56.93,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nope.}Cũng không.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.46,0:08:59.69,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ebola virus?}Virus Ebola?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.47,0:09:01.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{Nope.}Không.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.45,Main,,0,0,0,,{Bifidobacterium?}Bifidobacterium?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.04,0:09:05.73,Main,,0,0,0,,{Not even close.}Chẳng giống chút nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:07.30,Main,,0,0,0,,{What is it?}Là gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.01,0:09:09.82,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ein, you're being noisy.}Elin, trật tự nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.82,0:09:12.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{I can say for sure that\Nit wasn't an ordinary rat.}Chỉ có thể chắc chắn\Nđó không phải là chuột thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:14.50,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, keep it quiet.}Này, im lặng đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.12,Main,,0,0,0,,{So what is it?}Thế nó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:17.17,Main,,0,0,0,,{Well, it's...}Nó là...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.17,0:09:19.02,Main,,0,0,0,,{A mysterious space creature!}Sinh vật vũ trụ bí ẩn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.67,0:09:23.38,Main,,0,0,0,,{Spooky! The attack of\Na horrible space creature!}Sợ quá! Cuộc tấn công\Ncủa sinh vật đáng sợ ngoài không gian!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.42,0:09:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, there's that possibility...}Ừ, cũng là một khả năng.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:30.37,Main,,0,0,0,,{Heh... Yeah, right.}Khoan, mình nói gì thế này?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.37,0:09:31.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{Then what is it?}Vậy nó là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.84,0:09:33.67,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's not in the database.}Không có trong hệ thống dữ liệu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.51,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Ừ...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:36.47,Main,split,0,0,0,,{These base-pairs are weird, too.}Chuỗi ADN này cũng kỳ lạ nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.09,0:09:38.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{You think so?}Vậy à? Em nghĩ vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:40.56,Main,,0,0,0,,{We've never seen symptoms\Nlike this before either.}Ta cũng chưa từng thấy\Ntriệu chứng như thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.34,0:09:44.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Other than a space creature,\Nwhat is it? What is it?}Nếu không phải là sinh vật không gian\Nthì là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:50.25,Main,,0,0,0,,{Well... um, perhaps something like\Na rat went through a mutation}Có thể là chuột hoặc thứ gì đó đột biến
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.25,0:09:53.22,Main,,0,0,0,,{and evolved into some mysterious creature}thành một sinh vật bí ẩn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:56.43,Main,,0,0,0,,{and carried a mysterious poison...}và bây giờ xuất hiện độc tố bí ẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{What's that about?}Anh đang nói gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.97,0:10:01.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{That isn't too different from the\N"mysterious space creature" theory!}Thế có khác gì\Nso với sinh vật không gian bí ẩn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.03,0:10:02.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{This is too silly.}Đồ ngốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.61,Main,split,0,0,0,,{Aiya... what are we gonna do, Ein?}Ta làm gì đây, Elin?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.36,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It's a space creature!}Là sinh vật không gian đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.74,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's spooky!}Ma quái quá hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:49.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{All right. This is made to sense heat sources.}Được rồi. Cái này được thiết kế\Nđể cảm nhận nguồn nhiệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.41,0:10:53.79,Main,,0,0,0,,{It's usually used to find\Nbounties that are hiding.}Nó thường được sử dụng\Nđể truy tìm tội phạm đang lẩn trốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.06,0:10:55.75,Main,,0,0,0,,{Can you see me? [might need extra lead-in]}Thấy anh không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:06.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{All right, I'm gonna test it,\Nso move just like I tell you.}Được rồi, anh sẽ kiểm tra,\Ndi chuyển như anh hướng dẫn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.55,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ein! Where are you going?}Elin! Chạy đi đâu vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.55,0:11:10.64,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey, wait!}Này, đợi đã!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.64,0:11:11.41,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:16.78,Main,,0,0,0,,{That's weird... Is it broken?}Lạ thật. Nó bị hư rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.62,0:11:23.20,Main,,0,0,0,,{Was that response from you?}Nó bắt được thân nhiệt của cô à?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:27.49,Main,,0,0,0,,{That story you were telling, about some mysterious creature or something or other... [Wordy translation much? A lot of extra lead-out.]}Về sinh vật bí ẩn anh nói...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.34,0:11:27.49,Default - Alt,,0,0,0,,{Oh, yeah.}Ừ.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.49,0:11:29.71,Main,,0,0,0,,{What happens if you're bitten?}Nếu bị cắn thì sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:34.42,Main,,0,0,0,,{I can't say for sure until we catch\Nthe creature, but I'm going to guess...}Cho đến khi ta bắt được nó,\Ntôi không nói trước được gì, nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.03,0:11:35.96,Main,,0,0,0,,{...death?}Có bị chết không?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.17,0:11:41.13,Main,,0,0,0,,{No... why did it have to be this way?}Không thể nào.\NSao chuyện này lại xảy ra chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.13,0:11:43.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{I still have a lot to live for...}Tôi vẫn còn nhiều tâm nguyện\Nchưa hoàn thành.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.60,0:11:47.84,Main,,0,0,0,,{I haven't committed any crimes...}Tôi ngây thơ vô tội.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:53.06,Main,,0,0,0,,{I'm still young and lively...}Tôi vẫn còn trẻ và căng tràn sức sống.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.49,0:11:54.44,Main,,0,0,0,,{Lively?}Căng tràn sức sống?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:58.15,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh, poor little me!}Ôi, tội nghiệp tôi quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.05,0:12:01.11,Main,,0,0,0,,{Hey now, why are you getting into this?}Cả cô nữa ư? Cái quái gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.12,0:12:28.10,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{August 6th. Skyday.}{\i0}{\i1}Ngày 6 tháng 8. Ngày bầu trời.{\i0}
