Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.85,0:16:14.03,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ed! You aren't here, are you? Hey!}Ed. Em có ở đó chứ? Trả lời đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:23.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{Did that thing get her, too?}Nó cũng cắn cả đứa bé đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.04,Main,,0,0,0,,{Don't surprise me!}Đừng dọa tao như vậy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.21,0:17:08.54,Main,,0,0,0,,{I've been waiting for ya!}Tao đợi mày đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.85,0:17:18.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{Excellent!}Nhào vô!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.01,0:17:59.85,Main,,0,0,0,,{Come on, you slime!}Đến đây, sếp!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:05.89,Main,,0,0,0,,{Got 'im!}Bắt được mày rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:26.00,Main,,0,0,0,,{This thing seems familiar...}Nó làm mình nhớ đến một thứ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.46,0:18:32.59,Main,,0,0,0,,{I guess I shoulda eaten that.}Lẽ ra mình nên ăn nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.59,0:18:35.05,Main,,0,0,0,,{Oh yeah, it should be in the fridge—}Phải rồi, trong tủ lạnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.26,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{That was when I remembered everything.}{\i0}{\i1}Đó là lúc tôi nhớ ra mọi việc.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.17,0:18:45.97,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{It was... oh, one year ago.}{\i0}{\i1}Khoảng một năm trước.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:50.98,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{When I had gotten ahold of a real lobster,\NI hid it in the fridge in this stockroom}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi bắt được một con tôm hùm thật,{\i0}\N{\i1}để không bị người khác ăn mất,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.87,0:18:55.19,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{just so nobody else would eat it.}{\i0}{\i1}tôi đã giấu nó trong tủ lạnh ở nhà kho.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.83,0:18:59.40,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{But I had forgotten about it,\Nand left it in there for a whole year.}{\i0}{\i1}Nhưng tôi đã quên mất,{\i0}\N{\i1}và để nó ở đó cả năm trời.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.63,0:19:03.47,Main,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{I wonder what it looks like in there now...}{\i0}{\i1}Tôi tự hỏi bây giờ trông nó thế nào.{\i0}
